.TH LOA 1 "2026-03-31" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
loa \- command index for Library Of Alexandria
.SH SYNOPSIS
Use these commands inside the interactive prompt:
.br
alexandria> <command>
.SH DESCRIPTION
This page lists all available commands and where to find their dedicated man pages.
.SH COMMAND MANUALS
.TP
\fBadd\fR
add a new item (book or sheet music) (see \fBloa-add.1\fR)
.TP
\fBedit\fR
edit an item by reference (see \fBloa-edit.1\fR)
.TP
\fBdetails\fR
show detailed view for one item (see \fBloa-details.1\fR)
.TP
\fBbulk edit\fR
bulk\-update language/location/genre/tags/series on filtered items (see \fBloa-bulk-edit.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist\fR
list items with essential columns (see \fBloa-list.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist full\fR
list all columns for every item (see \fBloa-list-full.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist read\fR
list only read items (see \fBloa-list-read.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist unread\fR
list only unread items (see \fBloa-list-unread.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist sheet\fR
list only sheet music items (see \fBloa-list-sheet.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist genre <name>\fR
list items in a specific genre (see \fBloa-list-genre.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist language <name>\fR
list items in a specific language (see \fBloa-list-language.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist instrument <name>\fR
list sheet music by instrumentation (see \fBloa-list-instrument.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist tag <name>\fR
list items by tag (see \fBloa-list-tag.1\fR)
.TP
\fBsort by <field>\fR
sort by title | author | type | year | pages | language (see \fBloa-sort-by.1\fR)
.TP
\fBfind title\fR
search items by title (see \fBloa-find-title.1\fR)
.TP
\fBfind author\fR
search items by author (see \fBloa-find-author.1\fR)
.TP
\fBfind composer\fR
search sheet music by composer (see \fBloa-find-composer.1\fR)
.TP
\fBauthors\fR
list authors with counts and top genres/tags (see \fBloa-authors.1\fR)
.TP
\fBfind notes\fR
search full\-text notes (see \fBloa-find-notes.1\fR)
.TP
\fBsearch <query>\fR
advanced search (e.g. marx lang:german rating>=4 unread) (see \fBloa-search.1\fR)
.TP
\fBmetadata autofill [reference|all]\fR
fetch missing metadata from online sources with confirmation (see \fBloa-metadata-autofill.1\fR)
.TP
\fBdedup scan\fR
scan for likely duplicate items (see \fBloa-dedup-scan.1\fR)
.TP
\fBdedup merge\fR
merge two duplicate items (see \fBloa-dedup-merge.1\fR)
.TP
\fBdoctor [fix]\fR
validate data integrity and optionally auto\-fix common issues (see \fBloa-doctor.1\fR)
.TP
\fBcheck\fR
show one item by reference (see \fBloa-check.1\fR)
.TP
\fBremove\fR
remove an item by reference (see \fBloa-remove.1\fR)
.TP
\fBmark read\fR
mark an item as read by reference (see \fBloa-mark-read.1\fR)
.TP
\fBmark unread\fR
mark an item as unread by reference (see \fBloa-mark-unread.1\fR)
.TP
\fBnotes\fR
add or update notes by reference (see \fBloa-notes.1\fR)
.TP
\fBtag add\fR
add tags to an item (see \fBloa-tag-add.1\fR)
.TP
\fBtag remove\fR
remove tags from an item (see \fBloa-tag-remove.1\fR)
.TP
\fBtag set\fR
replace all tags on an item (see \fBloa-tag-set.1\fR)
.TP
\fBtag clear\fR
clear all tags from an item (see \fBloa-tag-clear.1\fR)
.TP
\fBrate\fR
set rating 1\-5 by reference (see \fBloa-rate.1\fR)
.TP
\fBprogress\fR
set reading progress (pages) by reference (see \fBloa-progress.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlanguage\fR
set language to German/English/French/Japanese by reference (see \fBloa-language.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlocation\fR
set location to Pforta or Zuhause by reference (see \fBloa-location.1\fR)
.TP
\fBpractice\fR
set sheet music practice status by reference (see \fBloa-practice.1\fR)
.TP
\fBpractice log\fR
log sheet\-music practice minutes and bpm (see \fBloa-practice-log.1\fR)
.TP
\fBpractice tempo\fR
set tempo target bpm for sheet music (see \fBloa-practice-tempo.1\fR)
.TP
\fBseries set\fR
set series name/index for one item (see \fBloa-series-set.1\fR)
.TP
\fBseries next [name]\fR
show next unread item per series or for one series (see \fBloa-series-next.1\fR)
.TP
\fBreading add\fR
add an item to reading list by reference (see \fBloa-reading-add.1\fR)
.TP
\fBreading list\fR
show reading list (see \fBloa-reading-list.1\fR)
.TP
\fBreading remove\fR
remove from reading list by reference (see \fBloa-reading-remove.1\fR)
.TP
\fBreading plan [weeks]\fR
build a weekly reading plan from capacity and progress (see \fBloa-reading-plan.1\fR)
.TP
\fBreading smart preview [count]\fR
preview smart recommendations based on interests (see \fBloa-reading-smart-preview.1\fR)
.TP
\fBreading smart generate [count]\fR
replace reading list with smart recommendations (see \fBloa-reading-smart-generate.1\fR)
.TP
\fBreading smart append [count]\fR
append smart recommendations to reading list (see \fBloa-reading-smart-append.1\fR)
.TP
\fBinterests set\fR
set smart recommendation interests (see \fBloa-interests-set.1\fR)
.TP
\fBinterests show\fR
show current smart recommendation interests (see \fBloa-interests-show.1\fR)
.TP
\fBinterests clear\fR
clear smart recommendation interests (see \fBloa-interests-clear.1\fR)
.TP
\fBsmart add\fR
create or update a smart list (see \fBloa-smart-add.1\fR)
.TP
\fBsmart list\fR
list all smart lists (see \fBloa-smart-list.1\fR)
.TP
\fBsmart run\fR
run a smart list (see \fBloa-smart-run.1\fR)
.TP
\fBsmart remove\fR
remove a smart list (see \fBloa-smart-remove.1\fR)
.TP
\fBgoal show\fR
show monthly and yearly goals (see \fBloa-goal-show.1\fR)
.TP
\fBgoal set monthly\fR
set monthly reading goal (see \fBloa-goal-set-monthly.1\fR)
.TP
\fBgoal set yearly\fR
set yearly reading goal (see \fBloa-goal-set-yearly.1\fR)
.TP
\fBgoal clear monthly\fR
clear monthly goal (see \fBloa-goal-clear-monthly.1\fR)
.TP
\fBgoal clear yearly\fR
clear yearly goal (see \fBloa-goal-clear-yearly.1\fR)
.TP
\fBcalendar add\fR
schedule reading/practice session (see \fBloa-calendar-add.1\fR)
.TP
\fBcalendar list [date]\fR
list scheduled sessions for one date (see \fBloa-calendar-list.1\fR)
.TP
\fBcalendar done\fR
mark one scheduled session as done (see \fBloa-calendar-done.1\fR)
.TP
\fBcalendar streak [reading|practice]\fR
show current completion streak (see \fBloa-calendar-streak.1\fR)
.TP
\fBinbox add\fR
quick\-capture unstructured item idea (see \fBloa-inbox-add.1\fR)
.TP
\fBinbox list\fR
list inbox items (see \fBloa-inbox-list.1\fR)
.TP
\fBinbox process\fR
convert inbox item into full library entry (see \fBloa-inbox-process.1\fR)
.TP
\fBinbox done\fR
mark inbox item as done (see \fBloa-inbox-done.1\fR)
.TP
\fBinbox remove\fR
remove inbox item (see \fBloa-inbox-remove.1\fR)
.TP
\fBsnapshot create [name]\fR
create named restore snapshot (see \fBloa-snapshot-create.1\fR)
.TP
\fBsnapshot list\fR
list available snapshots (see \fBloa-snapshot-list.1\fR)
.TP
\fBsnapshot restore\fR
restore state from snapshot (see \fBloa-snapshot-restore.1\fR)
.TP
\fBprofile show\fR
show active data profile (see \fBloa-profile-show.1\fR)
.TP
\fBprofile list\fR
list available profiles (see \fBloa-profile-list.1\fR)
.TP
\fBprofile new <name>\fR
create a new profile and switch to it (see \fBloa-profile-new.1\fR)
.TP
\fBprofile use <name>\fR
switch active profile (see \fBloa-profile-use.1\fR)
.TP
\fBai status\fR
show AI/Ollama integration status (see \fBloa-ai-status.1\fR)
.TP
\fBai mode [safe|fast]\fR
set AI safety mode (preview+approve or fast apply) (see \fBloa-ai-mode.1\fR)
.TP
\fBai model <name>\fR
set default Ollama model (see \fBloa-ai-model.1\fR)
.TP
\fBai recommend [count]\fR
show smart recommendations with explicit reasons (see \fBloa-ai-recommend.1\fR)
.TP
\fBai enrich [reference|all]\fR
generate summary/description/tags with preview+approve (see \fBloa-ai-enrich.1\fR)
.TP
\fBstats\fR
show collection and reading stats (see \fBloa-stats.1\fR)
.TP
\fBsheet stats\fR
show sheet music specific statistics (see \fBloa-sheet-stats.1\fR)
.TP
\fBbackup\fR
create backup file (see \fBloa-backup.1\fR)
.TP
\fBrestore\fR
restore from backup/export JSON (see \fBloa-restore.1\fR)
.TP
\fBexport\fR
export as JSON or CSV (see \fBloa-export.1\fR)
.TP
\fBexport obsidian <vault_path>\fR
export collection as Obsidian markdown vault notes (see \fBloa-export-obsidian.1\fR)
.TP
\fBobsidian\fR
show obsidian integration status and usage (see \fBloa-obsidian.1\fR)
.TP
\fBobsidian sync [vault_path]\fR
sync managed Alexandria notes into an Obsidian vault (see \fBloa-obsidian-sync.1\fR)
.TP
\fBobsidian doctor [vault_path]\fR
validate Obsidian vault path, write access, and folders (see \fBloa-obsidian-doctor.1\fR)
.TP
\fBobsidian open [book\-id|vault_path]\fR
open vault or jump directly to one managed note (see \fBloa-obsidian-open.1\fR)
.TP
\fBimport\fR
import from JSON or CSV (see \fBloa-import.1\fR)
.TP
\fBman <command>\fR
show bundled man page for a specific command (see \fBloa-man.1\fR)
.TP
\fBcompact [on|off|toggle]\fR
toggle compact table mode (see \fBloa-compact.1\fR)
.TP
\fBtheme [name|list|preview|set|clear|color]\fR
set theme, preview, and personalize colors (see \fBloa-theme.1\fR)
.TP
\fBundo\fR
undo last change (see \fBloa-undo.1\fR)
.TP
\fBhistory\fR
show command history (see \fBloa-history.1\fR)
.TP
\fBhelp [command]\fR
print help or command\-specific help (see \fBloa-help.1\fR)
.TP
\fBquit\fR
exit program (see \fBloa-quit.1\fR)
